            <scopecontent id="aspace_1a9e0ae093478d0a17ef6965afca90c9">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series contains minutes of various departmental and university committee meetings, and inner- and inter-departmental memos, form letters, and bulletins. Most of this material falls between 1965 and 1971, but some dates back to the 1950s. Also included in this series are: correspondence in reference to Sigma Chi, a science honorary fraternity; correspondence about departmental matters in general; the upkeep of the physical plant at the Engineering School; material about the Honeywell award; bursary material; Yale Studies for Returning Servicemen; miscellaneous topics similar to those listed above.</p>
