               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series, for the most part, consists of laboratory report books, copies of senior projects and Ph.D. dissertations. There also are some miscellaneous papers for various classes, published papers by former students, letters from several students discussing their dissertation progress, and ideas and problems that they are facing.</p>
